text.tspan: Template for laser training badge customization.
* Use the "namebadge" layer for your customization (ctrl-shift-l)
* Keep your customization inside the thick black box.
* Delete or hide the guidelines layer before saving.
* For vector lines (very thin) use a stroke width of 0.025mm (ctrl-shift-f)
* Convert fancy fonts to paths before saving
(select text object, path menu -> object to path.)
